<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<html xmlns:MadCap="http://www.madcapsoftware.com/Schemas/MadCap.xsd" MadCap:lastBlockDepth="3" MadCap:lastHeight="900" MadCap:lastWidth="688">
    <body>
        <div class="example">
            <p class="Example-Text">&#160;</p>
            <p>Let's say you want to open the Options dialog from the Tools menu. First, you press and release the <span class="Emphasis">ALT</span> key, which shows an underlined letter in each menu label.</p>
            <p>
                <img src="../../../Images/Contributor/Shortcuts/Alt-Shortcut-Keys-Menu1.png" alt="" title="" class="MaxWidth90Percent" />
            </p>
            <p>Press the <span class="Emphasis">T</span> key to open the Tools menu.</p>
            <p>
                <img src="../../../Images/Contributor/Shortcuts/Alt-Shortcut-Keys-Menu2.png" alt="" title="" class="MaxWidth90Percent" />
            </p>
            <p>Press the <span class="Emphasis">O</span> key.</p>
            <p>
                <img src="../../../Images/Contributor/Shortcuts/Alt-Shortcut-Keys-Menu3.png" alt="" title="" class="MaxWidth90Percent" />
            </p>
            <p>The Options dialog opens.</p>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>